-12-31T17:49:54.000Z","msg":"陸戰意大利同法國二揀一既話，邊個好啲?"},{"pid":"b1c4eddebdd3c5b133477ff11ad1172c321c5e0c","tid":1777510,"uid":67410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T18:40:04.000Z","msg":"12年岩岩開ser玩到而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"185a94cd02f6bec448b7660a85cd6b4d65fdb0fd","tid":1777510,"uid":253822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a155a4f4047b10b2182a2cc238fc17623373177","tid":1777510,"uid":34666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T17:49:54.000Z","msg":"陸戰意大利同法國二揀一既話，邊個好啲?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T19:37:40.000Z","msg":"意大利啲車好有特色<br />\n玩法唔同其他國家<br />\n娛樂性高<br />\n頂階公羊有成隻game最高穿嘅apfsds<br />\n仲要有oto防空<br />\n<br />\n法國就前期普普通通<br />\n維修費偏貴<br />\n頂階有leclerc<br />\n6s autoloader 有第二高穿嘅apfsds<br />\n但頂階lineup唔齊全<br />\n後備車不足"},{"pid":"f8ecf4df3343caf3b3f5befc32ed655b653cb3d8","tid":1777510,"uid":211446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T09:46:40.000Z","msg":"德國陸戰RB玩家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5454af2da462e9620a62649851b2687eb318bbfa","tid":1777510,"uid":103976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T05:33:09.000Z","msg":"RB 空戰 主要玩美德英螺旋槳<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f143da60c211295bfa56cdbac6cedbf3cf64152","tid":1777510,"uid":175108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5454af2da462e9620a62649851b2687eb318bbfa","tid":1777510,"uid":103976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T05:33:09.000Z","msg":"RB 空戰 主要玩美德英螺旋槳<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T03:12:23.000Z","msg":"德國機要玩hit and run冇得狗鬥唔夠頂癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b45430ed810efb1eb9c5e2cce90e10c6b97fc295","tid":1777510,"uid":10